<bibRefCitation author="Stahls" box="[681,880,1894,1919]" pageId="11" pageNumber="62" refString="Stahls, G., Ribeiro, E. &amp; Hanski, I. (1989) Fungivorous Pegomya flies: spatial and temporal variation in a guild of competitors. Annales zoologici fennici, 26, 103 - 112." type="journal article" year="1989">
Ståhls 
<emphasis box="[757,813,1894,1919]" italics="true" pageId="11" pageNumber="62">et al.</emphasis>
<number box="[820,880,1895,1919]" pageId="11" pageNumber="62" value="1989.0">1989</number>
